== Personal Projects

=== ProcVis _(TypeScript; HTML; Sass)_
#link("https://www.benjft.uk/ProcVis")[`benjft.uk/ProcVis`] #linebreak()
A web app to teach computer architecture. 
It emulates a Von Neumann processor with a simple instruction and visualizes 
the processes happening. 
It was intended to help teach by showing how the interactions that occur within 
the processor building intuition. 
Users are able to program the computer using its assembly language encouraging 
interaction.

